data.description: Recently renovated 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 car garage home located on a large private oversized lot. Updates include all new hurricane impact windows & doors throughout! Additional updates include, all new appliances (including washer/dryer), new A/C system, kitchen cabinets, granite counter tops, AC ducts replaced with new blown-in insulation, main bathroom, guest bathroom vanities, new laminate wood floors in living areas, new tile flooring in kitchen area, new light fixtures and hardware through out, new water heater, restored fireplace, screened patio, new concrete walkways, new water system (Kinetico), Swisstrax in garage. Property also includes a small storage shed. Please call for additional information to schedule a showing.
